Data.title: First Note
Data.descrition: Using responsive utility variants to build adaptive user interfaces. Overview Every utility class in Tailwind can be applied conditionally at different breakpoints, which makes it a piece of cake to build complex responsive interfaces without ever leaving your HTML.
